                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>Discover&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/content/dam/abbvie-dotcom/au/documents/the-value-of-hope-addressing-the-burden-of-ovarian-cancer-in-australia-report.pdf&quot;>&lt;i>The Value of Hope: Addressing the Burden of Ovarian Cancer in Australia&lt;/i>&lt;/a>, a comprehensive report developed by Deloitte Access Economics in partnership with AbbVie. This important resource shines a light on the significant impact of ovarian cancer on women, their families, and communities, highlighting the urgent need for advances in detection, treatment, and support.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
