                                    text="&lt;p>With fewer than half of those diagnosed surviving beyond five years&lt;sup>1&lt;/sup>, the report calls for increased investment in research, healthcare equity, and supportive care programs. Explore key insights and actionable recommendations to help improve outcomes for women affected by one of Australia’s most challenging and least understood cancers.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
