                                    sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                    text="&lt;p>''AbbVie supports ongoing collaboration to advance outcomes for women with ovarian cancer. We call on key health system stakeholders and decision makers to consider the recommendations presented in this important report.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>It’s our hope that Australia can improve its relative survival rates for ovarian cancer patients and reduce the overall socioeconomic burden on women, families, carers and the broader community impacted by ovarian cancer in the future&amp;quot;.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>&lt;b>Nathalie McNeil, Vice President and General Manager,&lt;/b>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;AbbVie Australia &amp;amp; New Zealand&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
